Si kastaba ha ahaatee, Bada Waqooyi waxaa ku wareegsan [[Aasiya|Waqooyiga qaarada Aasiya]] (inta ugu badan wadanka [[Ruushka]]), [[Yurub]] iyo [[Waqooyiga Ameerika]] (wadanka [[Kanada]] iyo [[Alaska|Gobolka Alaska]] ee [[Maraykanka]]). Tan iyo inta taariikhda lagu hayo biyaha Bada Arktik waxay ahaan jirtey ''biyo baraf'' ah, marka laga reebo [[xilli|xiliga gu'ga]] oo waxyar biyuhu diiri jireen. Sanadahan dambe waxaa isbedel weyn ku yimid [[heerkul]]kii lagu yaqaanay biyahan sababo la xidiidha [[cimilo|cimilada sii kululaanaysa]].<ref>[http://psc.apl.washington.edu/HLD/Lomo/OM2001AagaardWoodgate.pdf Some Thoughts on the Freezing and Melting of Sea Ice and Their Effects on the Ocean] K. Aagaard and R. A. Woodgate, Polar Science Center, Applied Physics Laboratory University of Washington, January 2001. Retrieved 7 December 2006.</ref> 

Guud ahaan Badweynta Arktik waxay leedahay [[biyo]] aad u badan oo saafi ah, si ka duwan biyaha badaha kale ee [[dhanaan]]ka ah waxay bada ku jira biyo nadiif ah oo baraf ah.


